dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents floodplains for Portland Metro, Oregon 1992. The dataset was originally published by the Metro Data Resource Center in February 2001.[100 Year Flood Plain as delineated by the Federal Emergency Management Association (FEMA). Digitized by the Portland Office of the Army Corps of Engineers.]
